fields.name: Regenerate Black Covers
fields.description: A bespoke set of 3D printed Regenerate Black covers from our Classic range, manufactured just for you. With our new magnetic location features, it's easier than ever to switch up your style to suit you. While we have tried to represent the colour and design of our covers as best we can, the final product you receive may have slight differences depending on your fitted arm.
